Enclosing class:
GridConcurrentLinkedQueue<E>
public static class GridConcurrentLinkedQueue.Node<E>
extends AtomicMarkableReference<GridConcurrentLinkedQueue.Node<E>>

Concurrent linked queue node. It can be effectively cleared (nullified) by calling GridConcurrentLinkedQueue.clearNode(Node) which allows to clear nodes without having to iterate through the queue. Note that clearing a node only nullifies its value and does not remove the node from the queue. To make sure that memory is reclaimed you must call GridConcurrentLinkedQueue.gc(int) explicitly.
